{"tid":874390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野外AV消滅？　畫面竟然被打格成咁","createTime":"2018-10-24T07:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T12:05:18.000Z","uid":72009,"like":231,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b078fd448314c439f0caef67dbc1878cd53764a3","tid":874390,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:09:54.000Z","msg":"AV女優川上奈奈美的新作，有一段牽著男優在街上購物的畫面，完全沒有任何性交的情節，結果整個畫面馬賽克「打好打滿」，只剩下男女優兩顆頭沒被key掉，兩顆頭飄來飄去交談，讓人看了很傻眼。<br />\n有人好奇問，「他們兩個又不會在街上打野砲，幹嘛搞成這樣？」，一劍浣春秋解釋，原來是因為之前有一部戶外拍攝的感謝祭作品，讓超過50人被移送法辦，雖然最後不起訴，但已令業界人心惶惶；加上日本民眾本來就很注重隱私，萬一有人發現自己成為了AV作品中的背景然後鬧大，片商與女優就吃不完兜著走了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20181024/1453435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20181024%2F1453435&d=XtradmV451CgdR%2FzWqTAFy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=791d38e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20181024%2F1453435&h=70710a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20181024/1453435</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_1e7ce844100c6631dbf8a8db7898b012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_1e7ce844100c6631dbf8a8db7898b012.jpg&h=a90e7652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_17332892014edfd6757c524825e1724c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_17332892014edfd6757c524825e1724c.jpg&h=bcbf2e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左膠，甚麼都管"},{"pid":"fe04e171f11eb608924b0a993d9b024c26726ba4","tid":874390,"uid":195169,"like":155,"dislike":1,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"獵奇笑片咁<img src